description: Infrea AB engages in investments in developing companies. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 378 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2018-04-20. The Company’s activities are concentrated within such segments as Land and Construction; Waste, Water and Sewage; as well as Fire Protection. Infrea AB acquires and develops unlisted companies on the Nordic countries market. The Company’s portfolio comprises: Asfaltsgruppen, which is engaged within paving; BST Brandskyddsteamet AB, the provider of sprinklers and fire protection systems; as well as Cleanpipe that conducts pipe inspections with cameras, sludge extraction and high pressure flushing for dry suction, wire lining, as well as transportation of hazardous waste and residual water.
name: Infrea AB
